body:
Let me clear this up at first, when i say low elo i mean low gold below (gold 5 - bronze 5)

I am writing this because i am sick of people letting games ALWAYS go 40 minutes plus and let these champions make a comeback and murder everyone in late game.

This is probably also the list of the best carry champions in the game.

#1 Yasuo.{{champion:157}}  
Yasuo is a very snowbally champion that excels in peoples mistakes, a talented yasuo is able to 1v9 carry most games, this serves as a double wammy since you dont have the chance of being destoried by one and won't have the chance to have a horrible one on your team.
They are also very annoying in all chat talking about their mistakes too often and just complain about how "stupid" over champions are but in reality yasuo is the stupider one.

Also it appears every top and midlaner in low elo and there mothers are mastery 7 yasuo and zed one tricks.


#2 Vayne.{{champion:67}} 
Your engagers can&#039;t engage, your toplaner building resistances is pointless when she has a blade of the ruined king, overall just a annoying champion to deal with in low elo.

#3 Caityln.{{champion:51}} 
This one may be a suprise but because games go on for so long in low elo caityln will always have the chance to scale up and be the most annoying adc to deal with because of her range.
The past 16 games i have played have all been carried by a caityln who did rubbish in lane.

#4 Illaoi.{{champion:420}} 
Lots of people who versed Illaoi have said &quot;whats the counterplay to this stuff&quot; in low elo SHE IS A MONSTER, because no one knows that cc or pure burst is her weakness.

#5 Fizz.{{champion:105}} 
People just do not know how to beat him in this elo and just tilt from fizz just standing there.

#6 Malphite/mumu.{{champion:54}} {{champion:32}} 
People just don&#039;t understand there is a malphite or a mumu in the game and they cannot be always clustered together.
